## Compliance Review — handoff + policy-driven approval
## Triage classifies risk, hands off high-risk items. Policy requires officer sign-off for high-risk reports.

### Submit a low-risk compliance request (completes automatically)
POST http://localhost:9000/compliance
Content-Type: application/json

{"request": "Annual review of employee handbook updates for office policy changes"}

### Submit a high-risk compliance request (triggers handoff + policy approval)
POST http://localhost:9000/compliance
Content-Type: application/json

{"request": "Review of new financial trading algorithm for regulatory compliance under MiFID II"}

### Check status — look for AWAITING_APPROVAL when officer sign-off is needed
GET http://localhost:9000/compliance/{{id}}

### Approve compliance finding
POST http://localhost:9000/compliance/{{id}}/approve

### Reject (task fails with the given reason)
POST http://localhost:9000/compliance/{{id}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{"reason": "Assessment needs to address cross-border data transfer implications"}
